It is little known, but Iczer-1 OVA got a movie cut after it has finished. It seems that up to this day, it has never been fully translated. And so here we present the first subbed release of Fight!! Iczer-1 Special Compilation.

R1 DVD script is used for most of the movie, with the extra lines having been translated by our usual suspects.. 
The movie cut is mostly made of the OVA footage joined together, but has some minor changes and few minutes of extra or reworked footage.
Basically, if you are a fan, you want to watch this.


